WEBVTT

00:03.640 --> 00:09.270
<font size="20"><b>Wall Maria contained one third
of humanity's remaining territory.</b></font>

00:10.360 --> 00:13.860
<font size="20"><b>Five years ago,
when humanity lost this territory,</b></font>

00:14.240 --> 00:17.470
<font size="20"><b>from within the remaining
two walls, they realized:</b></font>

00:18.330 --> 00:22.370
<font size="20"><b>"That we... are not meant to continue living."</b></font>

00:23.710 --> 00:28.010
<font size="20"><b>After all, humanity cannot defeat the Titans.</b></font>

00:28.960 --> 00:30.500
<font size="20"><b>I'm going to drive out...</b></font>

00:30.880 --> 00:34.970
<font size="20"><b>...every last one from this world!</b></font>

00:36.180 --> 00:40.940
<font size="20"><b>However, one young man gripped
that small blade held in his heart,</b></font>

00:41.640 --> 00:46.750
<font size="20"><b>and thrust it into a Titan, pounding its
massive head into the ground.</b></font>

00:47.980 --> 00:52.150
<font size="20"><b>When humanity saw this, what did they think?</b></font>

00:53.530 --> 00:55.320
<font size="20"><b>Some were proud.</b></font>

00:56.030 --> 00:57.870
<font size="20"><b>Some held hope.</b></font>

00:58.700 --> 01:01.200
<font size="20"><b>Some cried out in anger.</b></font>

01:02.790 --> 01:08.960
<font size="20"><b>Then, if Wall Maria was retaken,
what would humanity cry out?</b></font>

01:10.040 --> 01:15.050
<font size="20"><b>Would they finally start believing
that humanity deserves to live?</b></font>

01:15.310 --> 01:18.970
<font size="20"><b>Advance!</b></font>

01:21.890 --> 01:25.270
<font size="20"><b>That our own fate is something we can decide?</b></font>

01:26.020 --> 01:28.800
<font size="20"><b>Will it be enough for them to believe?</b></font>

01:30.520 --> 01:34.370
<font size="20"><b>If only Wall Maria was retaken...</b></font>

