03:09.960 --> 03:14.960
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}"The Town Where Everything Began"</b></font>

03:21.510 --> 03:22.510
<font size="20"><b>Whoa!</b></font>

03:22.510 --> 03:25.220
<font size="20"><b>Hey! You've gotta light up the ground!</b></font>

03:25.220 --> 03:26.660
<font size="20"><b>S-Sorry.</b></font>

03:27.010 --> 03:30.270
<font size="20"><b>We're not at the foot yet? It's almost dawn.</b></font>

03:30.270 --> 03:33.900
<font size="20"><b>Once we're over this mountain,
Shiganshina's right there.</b></font>

03:35.520 --> 03:37.780
<font size="20"><b>Sorry you're stuck with my horse.</b></font>

03:38.190 --> 03:40.740
<font size="20"><b>You're supposed to be saving your energy.</b></font>

03:40.740 --> 03:42.280
<font size="20"><b>Yeah, I know.</b></font>

03:42.280 --> 03:44.740
<font size="20"><b>She's right. Rest up, Eren.</b></font>

03:44.740 --> 03:46.410
<font size="20"><b>Don't say his name, idiot.</b></font>

03:46.410 --> 03:48.700
<font size="20"><b>Oh, yeah, sorry.</b></font>

03:48.700 --> 03:51.690
<font size="20"><b>Assume this place is swarming with enemies.</b></font>

03:53.920 --> 03:57.290
<font size="20"><b>Titan on the left! Everyone halt!
Light up the area!</b></font>

04:00.130 --> 04:02.600
<font size="20"><b>It's all right. He's fast asleep.</b></font>

04:02.600 --> 04:06.170
<font size="20"><b>This lad must not be one of those
new types that moves at night.</b></font>

04:07.430 --> 04:10.470
<font size="20"><b>That's too bad. Let him be.</b></font>

04:16.610 --> 04:19.940
<font size="20"><b>I can't believe we didn't
see it till that close up.</b></font>

04:19.940 --> 04:22.610
<font size="20"><b>Yeah, I'm with you there.</b></font>

04:22.610 --> 04:26.660
<font size="20"><b>This moonless night must be protecting us.</b></font>

04:26.660 --> 04:29.700
<font size="20"><b>Light from the moon is reflected sunlight.</b></font>

04:30.260 --> 04:31.620
<font size="20"><b>The new type of Titan...</b></font>

04:31.620 --> 04:36.430
<font size="20"><b>We think they use that minuscule
amount of reflected light to move.</b></font>

04:36.880 --> 04:39.380
<font size="20"><b>Using the new moon was the right move.</b></font>

04:40.170 --> 04:43.630
<font size="20"><b>There's no guarantee we won't
have a repeat of before.</b></font>

04:44.380 --> 04:48.420
<font size="20"><b>That lad may be one of those
"Moonlight Titans" for all we know.</b></font>

04:49.430 --> 04:52.270
<font size="20"><b>Hope we capture one someday!</b></font>

04:59.980 --> 05:01.250
<font size="20"><b>I'm shaking?</b></font>

05:02.570 --> 05:05.750
<font size="20"><b>Why? What am I so scared of?</b></font>

05:07.240 --> 05:08.240
<font size="20"><b>Shit...</b></font>

05:08.870 --> 05:12.450
<font size="20"><b>If I screw up retaking Wall Maria
because I'm like this, what then?!</b></font>

05:13.500 --> 05:15.880
<font size="20"><b>How many people will lose hope forever?</b></font>

05:16.370 --> 05:19.290
<font size="20"><b>There won't be a chance like this ever again!</b></font>

05:20.750 --> 05:23.020
<font size="20"><b>Am I not cut out for it after all?</b></font>

05:23.710 --> 05:28.140
<font size="20"><b>Someone like me? How can I save humanity?</b></font>

05:28.140 --> 05:30.640
<font size="20"><b>Someone like me? How?</b></font>

05:33.100 --> 05:34.390
<font size="20"><b>Eren...</b></font>

05:34.390 --> 05:38.600
<font size="20"><b>What are you shaking for? Are you scared?</b></font>

05:38.600 --> 05:40.860
<font size="20"><b>Huh?! I'm not scared!</b></font>

05:40.860 --> 05:44.280
<font size="20"><b>Huh? You're kidding... Look at your hand.</b></font>

05:44.440 --> 05:49.280
<font size="20"><b>This is... It's cold!
My hand's damn freezing!</b></font>

05:49.280 --> 05:53.650
<font size="20"><b>Really? My whole body's been
shaking this whole time.</b></font>

05:54.660 --> 05:55.600
<font size="20"><b>See?</b></font>

05:59.330 --> 06:02.220
<font size="20"><b>Eren, have you ever been afraid of Titans?</b></font>

06:04.000 --> 06:06.800
<font size="20"><b>Normally, everyone's terrified of them.</b></font>

06:07.130 --> 06:13.090
<font size="20"><b>Like me... The first time I faced a Titan,
I couldn't move a muscle.</b></font>

06:13.850 --> 06:16.420
<font size="20"><b>But... there I was...</b></font>

06:16.770 --> 06:19.390
<font size="20"><b>And you pulled me right out of a Titan's mouth.</b></font>

06:20.600 --> 06:23.760
<font size="20"><b>How were you able to do something like that?</b></font>

06:27.990 --> 06:29.260
<font size="20"><b>I remembered...</b></font>

06:29.990 --> 06:32.530
<font size="20"><b>...the time you showed me that book.</b></font>

06:33.990 --> 06:37.910
<font size="20"><b>Up until then, I never once thought
about what was outside the walls.</b></font>

06:39.330 --> 06:42.740
<font size="20"><b>I just spent every day
staring at the clouds and sky.</b></font>

06:44.630 --> 06:49.060
<font size="20"><b>But then, I heard your story
and looked into your eyes.</b></font>

06:51.090 --> 06:53.440
<font size="20"><b>You were seeing an awesome dream.</b></font>

06:54.090 --> 06:55.470
<font size="20"><b>But I had nothing.</b></font>

06:56.770 --> 06:58.730
<font size="20"><b>That's when I knew.</b></font>

06:59.440 --> 07:01.150
<font size="20"><b>I wasn't free.</b></font>

07:02.560 --> 07:07.900
<font size="20"><b>Trapped in a small cage in a huge world,
my freedom stolen by those unthinkable fiends.</b></font>

07:09.190 --> 07:12.960
<font size="20"><b>When I realized that, I couldn't forgive them.</b></font>

07:14.120 --> 07:18.800
<font size="20"><b>I don't know why, but when it
comes to taking back freedom...</b></font>

07:19.660 --> 07:23.220
<font size="20"><b>Yes... Strength flows through me.</b></font>

07:26.270 --> 07:27.460
<font size="20"><b>Thanks for that.</b></font>

07:27.960 --> 07:29.260
<font size="20"><b>I'm good now.</b></font>

07:29.260 --> 07:30.920
<font size="20"><b>Mmm.</b></font>

07:30.920 --> 07:36.260
<font size="20"><b>I bet, by this time next year,
we'll be looking at the sea.</b></font>

07:40.480 --> 07:42.940
<font size="20"><b>I recognize this area.</b></font>

07:45.150 --> 07:49.030
<font size="20"><b>I think... we came here for firewood.</b></font>

07:52.070 --> 07:54.700
<font size="20"><b>I can see the foot!</b></font>

07:54.700 --> 07:56.620
<font size="20"><b>There's signs of a trail!</b></font>

07:58.910 --> 08:01.250
<font size="20"><b>It's so close.</b></font>

08:01.250 --> 08:03.290
<font size="20"><b>I can hear the river.</b></font>

08:03.290 --> 08:06.590
<font size="20"><b>Finally, we're back...</b></font>

08:08.210 --> 08:11.760
<font size="20"><b>The first time... since we fled from here.</b></font>

08:13.050 --> 08:15.430
<font size="20"><b>Back to our hometown...</b></font>

08:32.360 --> 08:35.950
<font size="20"><b>Be on guard for Titans hiding in the shadows!</b></font>

08:35.950 --> 08:38.330
<font size="20"><b>Our operation begins now!</b></font>

08:38.330 --> 08:41.659
<font size="20"><b>All troops, switch to ODM gear!</b></font>

08:49.920 --> 08:54.340
<font size="20"><b>There's two gates we must seal--
the inner and outer.</b></font>

08:54.340 --> 08:56.640
<font size="20"><b>With that, Shiganshina will be isolated.</b></font>

08:56.640 --> 08:59.180
<font size="20"><b>We'll exterminate any Titans left inside.</b></font>

09:00.140 --> 09:04.180
<font size="20"><b>If the enemy knows our plan,
they'll go straight after Eren, but...</b></font>

09:08.980 --> 09:14.490
<font size="20"><b>We'll have hoods covering the faces
of all 100 of our soldiers.</b></font>

09:14.490 --> 09:19.410
<font size="20"><b>By the time they find out who Eren is,
we'll have the outer gate plugged.</b></font>

09:32.920 --> 09:34.920
<font size="20"><b>Don't stop!</b></font>

09:34.920 --> 09:37.380
<font size="20"><b>Head for the outer gate!</b></font>

09:37.380 --> 09:38.510
<font size="20"><b>Roger!</b></font>

09:43.390 --> 09:45.140
<font size="20"><b>This is...</b></font>

09:45.140 --> 09:47.060
<font size="20"><b>...the remains of a fire?</b></font>

09:50.860 --> 09:54.150
<font size="20"><b>They're here... and close!</b></font>

09:54.150 --> 09:56.110
<font size="20"><b>Bertholdt and Reiner!</b></font>

10:03.540 --> 10:06.290
<font size="20"><b>My house is right around there.</b></font>

10:06.290 --> 10:10.250
<font size="20"><b>That's where... we left everything behind.</b></font>

10:17.590 --> 10:20.550
<font size="20"><b>It's okay, I'll take it all back!</b></font>

10:24.560 --> 10:27.230
<font size="20"><b>This is all too strange...</b></font>

10:27.230 --> 10:30.190
<font size="20"><b>Not a single Titan in sight?</b></font>

10:30.190 --> 10:32.020
<font size="20"><b>But we have to keep going.</b></font>

10:32.020 --> 10:35.610
<font size="20"><b>Yeah, there's no reason to call it off.</b></font>

10:42.070 --> 10:45.870
<font size="20"><b>I can do this! No...</b></font>

10:45.870 --> 10:48.660
<font size="20"><b>We can do this!</b></font>

10:48.660 --> 10:54.290
<font size="20"><b>Because we've all been special
since the day we were born!</b></font>

10:54.290 --> 10:56.510
<font size="20"><b>We're free!</b></font>

11:15.980 --> 11:20.990
<font size="12" color="#000000"><b>{\an5}"Information Available for Public Disclosure"
"Glowing Ore"
"Ore harvested from the Reiss family's underground cavern. Thought to be produced by some sort of Titan power. It emits more light than a torch, and with appropriate manufacturing, can greatly extend nighttime operations."</b></font>

11:47.640 --> 11:49.930
<font size="20"><b>Don't let your guard down!</b></font>

11:49.930 --> 11:51.270
<font size="20"><b>Keep on the lookout!</b></font>

11:51.270 --> 11:52.480
<font size="20"><b>Roger!</b></font>

11:54.770 --> 11:55.730
<font size="20"><b>Eren!</b></font>

11:55.730 --> 11:57.980
<font size="20"><b>How's your ODM gear?</b></font>

11:57.980 --> 11:59.490
<font size="20"><b>It's fine.</b></font>

11:59.490 --> 12:02.610
<font size="20"><b>But I did manage to lose my cloak.</b></font>

12:07.740 --> 12:09.160
<font size="20"><b>Thanks.</b></font>

12:09.160 --> 12:10.870
<font size="20"><b>Mmm.</b></font>

12:10.870 --> 12:13.040
<font size="20"><b>The hole?!</b></font>

12:13.040 --> 12:14.500
<font size="20"><b>Success!</b></font>

12:15.540 --> 12:17.540
<font size="20"><b>It's plugged all right!</b></font>

12:21.130 --> 12:23.220
<font size="20"><b>We did it!</b></font>

12:23.220 --> 12:24.640
<font size="20"><b>Eren, you okay?</b></font>

12:24.640 --> 12:26.140
<font size="20"><b>No problems here.</b></font>

12:26.140 --> 12:27.930
<font size="20"><b>I'm ready like we trained.</b></font>

12:27.930 --> 12:29.770
<font size="20"><b>We'll head for the inner gate!</b></font>

12:29.770 --> 12:33.390
<font size="20"><b>While we're on the move,
remember to hide your faces!</b></font>

12:36.270 --> 12:40.400
<font size="20"><b>I really plugged the hole? And that easily...?</b></font>

12:40.400 --> 12:42.030
<font size="20"><b>You did it.</b></font>

12:42.030 --> 12:44.110
<font size="20"><b>Believe in your own power.</b></font>

12:46.950 --> 12:48.990
<font size="20"><b>The hole from then...</b></font>

12:51.750 --> 12:53.370
<font size="20"><b>Not yet!</b></font>

12:53.370 --> 12:58.130
<font size="20"><b>No matter how much you plug it,
they'll break the wall as long as they live.</b></font>

12:58.130 --> 13:01.760
<font size="20"><b>Until we kill Reiner, Bertholdt,
and any other enemies,</b></font>

13:01.760 --> 13:04.680
<font size="20"><b>the operation to retake Wall Maria won't end.</b></font>

13:04.680 --> 13:07.260
<font size="20"><b>Of course... I know that!</b></font>

13:09.260 --> 13:12.140
<font size="20"><b>The outer gate was a success.</b></font>

13:12.140 --> 13:14.640
<font size="20"><b>Still, it's odd...</b></font>

13:14.640 --> 13:16.810
<font size="20"><b>There's no attack coming.</b></font>

13:16.810 --> 13:21.860
<font size="20"><b>On the contrary, we've not seen
a single Titan so far.</b></font>

13:21.860 --> 13:25.450
<font size="20"><b>Were they not prepared for our sudden assault?</b></font>

13:25.450 --> 13:27.280
<font size="20"><b>We can only hope, but...</b></font>

13:27.280 --> 13:29.830
<font size="20"><b>Considering what Arlelt discovered...</b></font>

13:29.830 --> 13:31.700
<font size="20"><b>Hmm?</b></font>

13:31.700 --> 13:33.290
<font size="20"><b>I looked into it.</b></font>

13:33.290 --> 13:36.710
<font size="20"><b>I'm pretty sure someone was camping.</b></font>

13:36.710 --> 13:40.880
<font size="20"><b>The pot was cold and lights
were scattered on the ground.</b></font>

13:40.880 --> 13:43.710
<font size="20"><b>They were drinking something like black tea.</b></font>

13:45.260 --> 13:49.010
<font size="20"><b>Smells good... What is this drink?</b></font>

13:49.010 --> 13:53.470
<font size="20"><b>Also, there were three cups
with drops of a black liquid in it.</b></font>

13:53.470 --> 13:56.520
<font size="20"><b>At the least, there were
three people atop the wall.</b></font>

13:56.520 --> 13:58.850
<font size="20"><b>Th-Three, you say?!</b></font>

13:58.850 --> 14:01.270
<font size="20"><b>Was the metal pot completely cool?</b></font>

14:01.270 --> 14:02.190
<font size="20"><b>Yes.</b></font>

14:02.190 --> 14:03.530
<font size="20"><b>I find that odd.</b></font>

14:03.530 --> 14:04.440
<font size="20"><b>Agreed.</b></font>

14:04.440 --> 14:07.240
<font size="20"><b>Th-The pot?</b></font>

14:07.240 --> 14:12.790
<font size="20"><b>We charged here at full speed
using horses and ODM gear.</b></font>

14:12.790 --> 14:17.120
<font size="20"><b>Had they noticed our approach
by sound or by sight,</b></font>

14:17.120 --> 14:19.790
<font size="20"><b>they'd have two minutes to react.</b></font>

14:19.790 --> 14:24.050
<font size="20"><b>A pot in use wouldn't cool in just two minutes.</b></font>

14:24.050 --> 14:28.340
<font size="20"><b>They had to have known we were
coming for five minutes or more.</b></font>

14:28.340 --> 14:31.970
<font size="20"><b>Meaning they've had plenty
of time to prepare for us.</b></font>

14:31.970 --> 14:34.180
<font size="20"><b>But... how?</b></font>

14:34.180 --> 14:39.020
<font size="20"><b>Th-There must be a scout in addition
to the three on the wall...</b></font>

14:39.020 --> 14:43.900
<font size="20"><b>No, we have to assume there's
many more enemies in hiding.</b></font>

14:43.900 --> 14:47.110
<font size="20"><b>For now, locating the enemy is our priority.</b></font>

14:47.110 --> 14:48.400
<font size="20"><b>Arlelt...</b></font>

14:48.400 --> 14:52.950
<font size="20"><b>With that brain of yours, you've saved
us from disaster countless times.</b></font>

14:52.950 --> 14:56.250
<font size="20"><b>Right now is one of those times we need you.</b></font>

14:56.250 --> 14:58.120
<font size="20"><b>Huh?</b></font>

14:58.120 --> 15:00.210
<font size="20"><b>Take as many soldiers as needed.</b></font>

15:00.210 --> 15:03.500
<font size="20"><b>Find out if enemies are hiding
near the inner gate or not.</b></font>

15:05.800 --> 15:09.300
<font size="20"><b>As of now, you obey Armin Arlelt's commands.</b></font>

15:09.300 --> 15:11.300
<font size="20"><b>Continue the search!</b></font>

15:15.890 --> 15:16.720
<font size="20"><b>R...</b></font>

15:16.720 --> 15:17.890
<font size="20"><b>Roger!</b></font>

15:17.890 --> 15:19.980
<font size="20"><b>We searched the wall thoroughly!</b></font>

15:19.980 --> 15:22.270
<font size="20"><b>What are your orders, Arlelt?!</b></font>

15:24.230 --> 15:26.570
<font size="20"><b>Send one group to each side of the wall!</b></font>

15:26.570 --> 15:29.190
<font size="20"><b>Search all the buildings near the inner gate!</b></font>

15:29.190 --> 15:31.910
<font size="20"><b>Report any findings with an acoustic shell!</b></font>

15:33.240 --> 15:36.490
<font size="20"><b>A-All right?</b></font>

15:36.490 --> 15:37.750
<font size="20"><b>Roger!</b></font>

15:41.830 --> 15:43.630
<font size="20"><b>Another big gamble of yours?</b></font>

15:43.630 --> 15:46.670
<font size="20"><b>No, he's proven himself.</b></font>

15:46.670 --> 15:49.920
<font size="20"><b>He's one of our greatest weapons.</b></font>

15:49.920 --> 15:52.630
<font size="20"><b>Eren's coming to plug the inner gate.</b></font>

15:52.630 --> 15:54.050
<font size="20"><b>What now?</b></font>

15:54.050 --> 15:57.010
<font size="20"><b>Pause the operation until we find the enemy?</b></font>

15:58.810 --> 16:00.980
<font size="20"><b>We continue.</b></font>

16:00.980 --> 16:04.360
<font size="20"><b>We'll lose a prolonged battle
in enemy territory.</b></font>

16:04.360 --> 16:08.730
<font size="20"><b>For us, our only chance
is with a decisive battle.</b></font>

16:08.730 --> 16:14.990
<font size="20"><b>Besides, if this is all according to the
enemy's plan, we'll just have to live with it.</b></font>

16:14.990 --> 16:19.790
<font size="20"><b>In any case, they're not the
only ones hiding something.</b></font>

16:26.340 --> 16:28.590
<font size="20"><b>What do I do?</b></font>

16:28.590 --> 16:32.010
<font size="20"><b>Eren's coming to seal the inner gate...</b></font>

16:32.010 --> 16:34.680
<font size="20"><b>And we don't know where the enemy's at!</b></font>

16:35.760 --> 16:39.810
<font size="20"><b>Why haven't they shown
even though we plugged the wall?</b></font>

16:39.810 --> 16:43.640
<font size="20"><b>Why can't we find them
no matter how much we search?</b></font>

16:43.640 --> 16:46.060
<font size="20"><b>This is bad... What now?</b></font>

16:46.060 --> 16:49.730
<font size="20"><b>If we fail... that'll really be the end!</b></font>

16:49.730 --> 16:52.610
<font size="20"><b>It's over. Everything...</b></font>

16:52.610 --> 16:57.200
<font size="20"><b>They always attack us in unthinkable
ways we always fail to predict.</b></font>

16:57.200 --> 16:59.580
<font size="20"><b>We're always at a disadvantage because...</b></font>

16:59.580 --> 17:02.870
<font size="20"><b>...we simply know nothing about Titans!</b></font>

17:03.910 --> 17:05.500
<font size="20"><b>Always...?</b></font>

17:21.810 --> 17:23.430
<font size="20"><b>Did you find them, Arlelt?!</b></font>

17:23.430 --> 17:24.390
<font size="20"><b>Where are they?!</b></font>

17:24.390 --> 17:27.349
<font size="20"><b>Not yet! Everyone search the walls!</b></font>

17:27.349 --> 17:29.270
<font size="20"><b>I told you we already did!</b></font>

17:29.270 --> 17:30.900
<font size="20"><b>There's nowhere to hide!</b></font>

17:30.900 --> 17:32.650
<font size="20"><b>Inside the walls!</b></font>

17:33.820 --> 17:35.150
<font size="20"><b>Inside the walls?</b></font>

17:35.150 --> 17:36.320
<font size="20"><b>Yes!</b></font>

17:36.320 --> 17:40.410
<font size="20"><b>There must be a spot where someone
could stay inside for a long time!</b></font>

17:40.410 --> 17:42.330
<font size="20"><b>How do you know that?!</b></font>

17:45.160 --> 17:46.290
<font size="20"><b>It's a hunch.</b></font>

17:47.170 --> 17:50.590
<font size="20"><b>Do you have any idea what
sort of situation we're in?!</b></font>

17:50.590 --> 17:53.010
<font size="20"><b>We don't have time to waste on hunches!</b></font>

17:53.010 --> 17:54.670
<font size="20"><b>Think about it!</b></font>

17:54.670 --> 17:59.350
<font size="20"><b>The enemy always attacks us using
Titan powers in ways we never imagine!</b></font>

17:59.350 --> 18:02.430
<font size="20"><b>If we constrain ourselves to
common sense and reason,</b></font>

18:02.430 --> 18:05.430
<font size="20"><b>we'll never be able to gain the upper hand!</b></font>

18:13.900 --> 18:16.150
<font size="20"><b>The signal to halt the mission!</b></font>

18:16.150 --> 18:19.030
<font size="20"><b>All troops, scatter and stand by atop the wall!</b></font>

18:19.030 --> 18:20.490
<font size="20"><b>Roger!</b></font>

18:22.120 --> 18:25.750
<font size="20"><b>There are times to be strict
and times to be flexible.</b></font>

18:25.750 --> 18:30.000
<font size="20"><b>Adhere to the principles you vowed
while giving everything you've got.</b></font>

18:30.000 --> 18:32.210
<font size="20"><b>Obey the chain of command.</b></font>

18:32.210 --> 18:35.260
<font size="20"><b>The reason we are here is to claim victory!</b></font>

18:37.800 --> 18:40.680
<font size="20"><b>Break into two groups again
and search the surface!</b></font>

18:40.680 --> 18:42.640
<font size="20"><b>Especially above the gate!</b></font>

18:42.640 --> 18:44.470
<font size="20"><b>Commence the search!</b></font>

18:45.520 --> 18:46.390
<font size="20"><b>Rog...</b></font>

18:46.390 --> 18:47.770
<font size="20"><b>Roger!</b></font>

18:55.230 --> 18:57.150
<font size="20"><b>What are they doing?</b></font>

18:57.150 --> 19:00.110
<font size="20"><b>Should we really be waiting like this?</b></font>

19:00.110 --> 19:03.950
<font size="20"><b>Yeah, so much for our surprise attack...</b></font>

19:04.910 --> 19:08.370
<font size="20"><b>Armin... Did you figure something out?</b></font>

19:16.420 --> 19:21.050
<font size="20"><b>A position to react, no matter
when Eren appears...</b></font>

19:21.050 --> 19:24.100
<font size="20"><b>A position able to see everything...</b></font>

19:24.100 --> 19:28.390
<font size="20"><b>If there is such a place,
it has to be in the walls.</b></font>

19:28.390 --> 19:32.770
<font size="20"><b>If the enemy has no idea we know
about the Titans in the walls,</b></font>

19:32.770 --> 19:36.070
<font size="20"><b>and they think we'll never see it coming...</b></font>

19:36.070 --> 19:37.400
<font size="20"><b>Or possibly...?</b></font>

19:44.160 --> 19:47.040
<font size="20"><b>Here! There's a cavity here!</b></font>

19:59.050 --> 20:00.380
<font size="20"><b>Reiner!</b></font>

20:18.440 --> 20:19.400
<font size="20"><b>Shit!</b></font>

20:19.400 --> 20:20.030
<font size="20"><b>--Captain?!</b></font>

20:20.030 --> 20:20.690
<font size="20"><b>--Is that another Titan power?!
--Captain?!</b></font>

20:20.690 --> 20:21.860
<font size="20"><b>--Is that another Titan power?!</b></font>

20:21.860 --> 20:25.370
<font size="20"><b>So close! But I couldn't finish 'em!</b></font>

20:43.130 --> 20:45.340
<font size="20"><b>Keep on the lookout!</b></font>

20:45.340 --> 20:47.260
<font size="20"><b>Locate his allies!</b></font>

21:23.050 --> 21:24.800
<font size="20"><b>Boulder incoming!</b></font>

21:24.800 --> 21:26.760
<font size="20"><b>Get down!</b></font>

21:31.180 --> 21:32.390
<font size="20"><b>What the--?!</b></font>

21:32.390 --> 21:34.020
<font size="20"><b>Did he miss?</b></font>

21:34.020 --> 21:37.900
<font size="20"><b>No... That was good aim.</b></font>

21:37.900 --> 21:43.070
<font size="20"><b>He plugged the entrance.
Now the horses can't pass.</b></font>

21:43.070 --> 21:45.490
<font size="20"><b>They'll aim for the horses and surround us...</b></font>

21:45.490 --> 21:50.080
<font size="20"><b>...in order to block our escape
and annihilate us here.</b></font>

21:50.080 --> 21:52.950
<font size="20"><b>We're both hoping for the same thing.</b></font>

21:52.950 --> 21:56.040
<font size="20"><b>To settle it here once and for all.</b></font>

21:56.040 --> 21:58.210
<font size="20"><b>Humanity or Titans?!</b></font>

21:58.210 --> 22:02.420
<font size="20"><b>Which side will live?! Which side will perish?!</b></font>

23:41.020 --> 23:44.650
<font size="20"><b>A horde of Titans appears out of nowhere.</b></font>

23:44.650 --> 23:46.940
<font size="20"><b>As they vie to settle the fight,</b></font>

23:46.940 --> 23:53.370
<font size="20"><b>the once friend becomes enemy
and stands in Eren's way.</b></font>

23:53.370 --> 23:56.590
<font size="20"><b>Next episode: "Thunder Spears."</b></font>

